From: Richard Acayan <mailingradian@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:46:04 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 056/194] hack! ASoC: qdsp6: q6voice-dai: add tdm

The TDM ports are used on the Pixel 3a for built-in speaker, earpiece,
and microphone. Add support for them in the voice call audio driver.

Signed-off-by: Richard Acayan <mailingradian@gmail.com>
